quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  17,100,"Say [to them], "
  17,101,"And We had certainly given Moses nine evident signs, so ask the Children of Israel [about] when he came to them and Pharaoh said to him, "
  17,102,"[Moses] said, ",1:[i.e., I am certain.]
  18,67,"He said, "
  18,68,"And how can you have patience for what you do not encompass in knowledge?"
  18,69,"[Moses] said, "
  19,28,"O sister [i.e., descendant] of Aaron, your father was not a man of evil, nor was your mother unchaste."
  19,29,"So she pointed to him. They said, "
  19,30,"[Jesus] said, "
  20,10,"When he saw a fire and said to his family, "
  20,11,"And when he came to it, he was called, "
  20,12,"Indeed, I am your Lord, so remove your sandals. Indeed, you are in the blessed valley of Ṭuwā."